# Binaries for programs and plugins
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binary, built with `go test -c`
*.test

# Output of the go coverage tool, specifically when used with LiteIDE
*.out

# Dependency directories (remove the comment below to include it)
# vendor/
.vscode/
dist/
target/
# codegen/ is regenerated from the OpenAPI spec by `go generate ./...`
# (see main.go). custom.go is hand-written though — it carries types
# we attach to the generated package without modifying the generator
# template. The `codegen/*` form (rather than `codegen/`) lets the
# `!codegen/custom.go` re-inclusion below take effect.
codegen/*
!codegen/custom.go
codegen/message_bus/
__debug_bin
CasaOS-AppManagement 

# node_modules
node_modules
package-lock.json

.idea
build/sysroot/usr/bin/appfile2compose
